menuconfig MODULES_WP_HASH_CHAIN
	bool "wp_hash_chain"
	default n
	---help---
		Waypoint hash chain using OP-TEE TrustZone.
		Hashes planned waypoint coordinates (from navigator_mission_item)
		each time mission_result.seq_reached advances — i.e. exactly when
		the drone marks a waypoint as reached.
		Results published as wp_hash_chain topic and saved to
		wp_flight_chain.sha256 on landing for comparison with the
		ground-station planned chain.
